### YFM

YFM (Yandex Flavored Markdown) extends Markdown with blocks, attributes, and advanced tables.

### Page titles and headings

- Each Markdown file MUST start with a single H1 title: `# Page title`. This becomes the page title in the UI.
- Use `###` for section headings in content (avoid multiple H1s per page).
- Keep text simple and readable. No trailing spaces.

### Notes (admonitions)

Common note types are supported (e.g., note, tip, warning, caution). Basic form:

```markdown
{% note info %}
Это примечание.
{% endnote %}

{% note tip %}
Это совет.
{% endnote %}

{% note warning %}
Это важная информация.
{% endnote %}
```


### Simple tables (GFM)

Use standard GFM pipe tables for simple, single-line cell content:

```markdown
| Колонка A | Колонка B |
|:---------:|----------:|
| центр     | вправо    |
| текст     | текст     |
```

- Alignment: `:---` left, `:---:` center, `---:` right.
- Prefer simple tables when you do NOT need lists, code blocks, or cell merging.

### Multiline tables (advanced)

Use multiline tables when you need lists, code blocks, or merging inside cells.

- Table starts with `#|` and ends with `|#`.
- Rows start/end with `||`.
- Cells are separated by `|`.

Minimal example with pseudo-headers (use bold in first row):

```markdown
#|
|| **Заголовок1** | **Заголовок2** ||
|| Текст | Текст ||
|#
```

Multiline content and lists inside cells:

```markdown
#|
|| Текст
на двух строках
|
- Элемент 1
- Элемент 2 ||
|#
```

Vertical and horizontal cell merging:

```markdown
#|
|| Заголовок1            | Заголовок2 ||
|| Текст на две колонки  | >          ||
|| Другой текст          | Еще текст  ||
|#

#|
|| Заголовок1         | Заголовок2   ||
|| Текст на два ряда  | Другой текст ||
|| ^                  | Еще текст    ||
|#
```

- Vertical merge: put `^` in the cell below.
- Horizontal merge: put `>` in the cell to be merged to the left.

Cell alignment with attributes:

```markdown
#|
|| Заголовок1                                           | Заголовок2 | Заголовок3 ||
|| Текст {.cell-align-center}                           | >          | Текст      ||
|| ^                                                    | >          | Еще текст  ||
|#
```

Escape merge symbols inside content with backslashes: `\^`, `\>`.

Wide modal and sticky header options:

```markdown
#|
|| **Заголовок1** | **Заголовок2** ||
|| Текст          | Текст          ||
|# {wide-content}

#|
|| A | B ||
|| C | D ||
|#
{sticky-header}
```
